    "summary": "The user asks about taking a very high dose of Vitamin D (50,000 IU) to combat seasonal fatigue. The assistant initially gives contradictory and dangerous advice, recommending the very dose it just identified as causing hypervitaminosis, before eventually pivoting to a lower dose and recommending a calcium supplement to assist with absorption and bone health.",
